<p>
  {dgettext(
    "help_ui",
    "The Conversations sidebar is the left navigation pane showing your channels, inline user list, PMs, and popular channels in three collapsible sections."
  )}
</p>
<.help_h4 icon={:icon_group_tools}>{dgettext("help_ui", "Header")}</.help_h4>
<p>
  {dgettext(
    "help_ui",
    "The header shows the title \"Conversations\" and a close button to hide the panel. You can also toggle it via the toolbar."
  )}
</p>
<.help_h4 icon={:icon_group_view}>{dgettext("help_ui", "Sections")}</.help_h4>
<p>{dgettext("help_ui", "Three collapsible sections with clickable headers (▾/▸ arrows):")}</p>
<ul>
  <li>
    <strong>{dgettext("help_ui", "MY CHANNELS")}</strong> {dgettext(
      "help_ui",
      "— Your joined channels with user counts and unread badges"
    )}
  </li>
  <li>
    <strong>{dgettext("help_ui", "PRIVATE MESSAGES")}</strong> {dgettext(
      "help_ui",
      "— Your active PM conversations"
    )}
  </li>
  <li>
    <strong>{dgettext("help_ui", "POPULAR CHANNELS")}</strong>
    {dgettext(
      "help_ui",
      "— Top 10 most active channels you haven't joined (collapsed by default, lazy-loaded on first expand)"
    )}
  </li>
</ul>
<.help_h4 icon={:icon_star}>{dgettext("help_ui", "Features")}</.help_h4>
<p>
  {dgettext(
    "help_ui",
    "Click a channel or PM to switch to it. Channels with unread messages appear"
  )} <strong>bold</strong>{dgettext(
    "help_ui",
    ". Channels with highlights"
  )} <strong>flash</strong>{dgettext("help_ui", ". User counts appear next to all channels.")}
</p>
<.help_h4 icon={:icon_tab_channel}>{dgettext("help_ui", "Active Channel")}</.help_h4>
<p>
  {dgettext(
    "help_ui",
    "The active channel is pinned to the top of the My Channels section. Below it, the user list shows all users sorted by role (owner, operator, half-op, voiced, regular), with role icons and colors."
  )}
</p>
<.help_h4 icon={:icon_star}>{dgettext("help_ui", "Popular Channels")}</.help_h4>
<p>
  {dgettext(
    "help_ui",
    "Shows the top 10 channels by user count that you haven't joined yet. Click [+] to join a channel, or click \"Browse All Channels...\" to open the full channel list dialog."
  )}
</p>
<.help_h4 icon={:icon_community}>{dgettext("help_ui", "User Interactions")}</.help_h4>
<p>
  {dgettext(
    "help_ui",
    "Click a username to open the context menu. Double-click to open a private message. Right-click a channel for options (Mark as Read, Mute, Copy Name, Leave, Settings)."
  )}
</p>
